# Tzatziki Sauce

> A Greek staple. Perfect for grilled chicken or falafel. #sauce

- Greek Yogurt | Plain, 4 oz | 
- Cucumber | 1/2 | Peeled, Seeded, and Diced
- Olive Oil | 1 1/2 tsp | 
- Lemon | 1/8 | Juiced
- Pepper | Black, to taste | Freshly Ground
- Dill | Fresh, 1/2 tbsp | Chopped
- Garlic | 1 clove | Peeled
